headline: 2 HMO Stocks Poised to Thrive Despite Escalating Medical Costs
summary: The Medical-HMO industry benefits from strength in commercial plans, M&A and expected Medicare rate hikes, but rising costs, regulatory shifts and workforce shortages strain margins. CI and HUM are likely to navigate industry storms.
